short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirect DRG Fandom Requests to DRG wiki

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tired of bad Fandom wiki that are either out of date or just filled with wrong information? Well search no more. This plugin was created to finally remove the fandom results from our google search!

You can toggle it on and off. While the plugin is active, clicking on a fandom link will redirect you to the official "wiki.gg"! Even if your friend sends you a fandom page from fandom, you'll be redirected! With that plugin also comes an option to remove the fandom result from the google search too! How amazing.

No more being scared of fandom.
